{"tid":1537350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩藉口可以推左返大陸參觀嘅trip","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T02:43:10.000Z","uid":12805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"23516a22e0264155e37538b21d2a11e4d2c1995d","tid":1537350,"uid":12805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"想推撚左佢，佢又寫住must返去，但係扮病又好似唔啱數，唔想返去大陸呢啲鬼地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29e702471d361894811d404470d430d5c9d718b","tid":1537350,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:48:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"800554c4d1bf97bc5e1b404fde8aa5d44b74c251","tid":1537350,"uid":254388,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c26735f3e75f403a1760277c85a0a5af2bf7451b","tid":1537350,"uid":20244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:49:13.000Z","msg":"辭職，要返大陸都係垃圾工"},{"pid":"188cfa3a97e91aec8f9a1f7ebd8fcc1cd680d94b","tid":1537350,"uid":84259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:49:33.000Z","msg":"無回鄉證"},{"pid":"ff8002a50f0d36227fa3a53e485aedcac78df864","tid":1537350,"uid":254388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:50:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae08a636c2aad6aa8b8d489938f6830ee37bc51c","tid":1537350,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:53:06.000Z","msg":"無回鄉證,完"},{"pid":"0a8d7b49faefec4e4bd7d3d7bd3561a9a6311204","tid":1537350,"uid":174502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:56:06.000Z","msg":"型d:返大陸會俾捉，不了<br />\n柒d:我回鄉證過期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e75d73691fa4614054c03ddda5190dfb70eb6e2","tid":1537350,"uid":294844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:57:40.000Z","msg":"你冇辭職既勇氣講黎拖柒，疊埋心水去大陸喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebf807a3c899f0c28b1da5c890e80637da22cbe","tid":1537350,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:00:55.000Z","msg":"睇醫生拎病紙"},{"pid":"e51185645eb3121c7c4de7408596c4aa366c8bd6","tid":1537350,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"同佢講俾人抄過牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7529d1c3f95b7288727d699be67e73c9ae745ae","tid":1537350,"uid":36072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:04: